{"tid":2157658,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"官︰警證供出入大 無法倚賴  工程師脫藏電鑽等三罪","createTime":"2020-08-15T07:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T07:32:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5ac2156c251e5e6be5fe4998667e375b79c1844e","tid":2157658,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:31:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/RH6EPHM3QJG3FDVNSHPYW4R3TU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2FRH6EPHM3QJG3FDVNSHPYW4R3TU%2F&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8ef4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=0a59f9c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2FRH6EPHM3QJG3FDVNSHPYW4R3TU%2F&h=08e22fde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/RH6EPHM3QJG3FDVNSHPYW4R3TU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n官︰警證供出入大 無法倚賴 <br />\n工程師脫藏電鑽等三罪<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】昨有兩名反修例案的被告經審訊後脫罪，其中一名年輕工程師被指藏有電鑽、電磨機、鎚仔、無線電通訊器等物品被控，經過半日審訊，裁判官何俊堯隨即裁決，指兩名警員證供有重大出入，認為無法倚賴警員證供，裁定被告所有控罪罪脫。另一宗案被告因藏有士巴拿和行山杖被控，裁判官林子勤指被告非但沒提出用涉案工具來傷人，而是因擔心遇上「白衣人」、「刀手」，為避免使用武力才管有，裁定罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。，旁聽人士聞判即鼓掌，部份人更在散庭後上前與被告擁抱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CQ9Rbf0Miixfo2d-LwouL64I_Gk=/1718x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6XSG7L2WLRCK5FAPYFMPF677TE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCQ9Rbf0Miixfo2d-LwouL64I_Gk%3D%2F1718x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6XSG7L2WLRCK5FAPYFMPF677TE.jpg&h=91f6c835&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被告陳俊賢昨由支持者護送下離開法院。<br />\n<br />\n據防暴警李家駿證供，去年11月2日，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n帶行山杖防刀手 被告甩罪<br />\n<br />\n有關背囊套問題，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。至於無牌管有無線電通訊器具罪，何官指兩名控方證人都沒提及從被告身上搜出無線電通訊器，何官指控方沒提供被告管有相關物品的證據，裁定表面證供不成立。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。被告非但沒有提出用涉案工具來傷人，而是為避免使用武力，使大家在安全的情況下離開，才管有工具，裁定被告管有攻擊性武器罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC720 、WKCC1241/20"},{"pid":"2a4ceb2efe5538d6840b5bcdda0f4d5a817b71dc","tid":2157658,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:32:04.000Z","msg":"大家要定時定候捐款去 612基金，長期作戰嚟。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2142357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2142357</a>"},{"pid":"8b0b0eb699e5c3d3aeb757e7403fc4bc390c7727","tid":2157658,"uid":234457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:32:05.000Z","msg":"咁驚制裁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"2a4ceb2efe5538d6840b5bcdda0f4d5a817b71dc","tid":2157658,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:32:04.000Z","msg":"大家要定時定候捐款去 612基金，長期作戰嚟。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2142357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2142357</a>"}}